#### **QUESTION B (14 Marks)**  *(Alternative Choice)*

> **[KTU University Exam – Sample 2024 Scheme]**

**(a) [7 Marks]** Demonstrate **exception handling** for an "insufficient balance" scenario in a `BankAccount` class. Write equivalent implementations in **Java (checked exception)** and **Python (custom exception)**.

**(b) [7 Marks]** Explain with code examples how **lambda expressions** differ syntactically in **C++11, Java 8, and Python**.

